{"word":"ἀπέχθομαι","slug":"ἀπέχθομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n12032\" key=\"a)pe/xqomai\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀπέχθ-ομαι</orth>, later form of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀπεχθάνομαι,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0005.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:45\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Theoc.\">Theoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.45</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lyc.\">Lyc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">116</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">AP</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.176</biblScope> </bibl> (<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Mel.\">Mel.</a></author> </bibl>), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0007.tlg022:22\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Marc.\">Marc.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; for in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg005.perseus-grc1:1260\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hipp.\">Hipp.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1260</biblScope> </bibl> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπάχθομαι</foreign> is the better reading; and the <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ inf.\">inf.</a></mood> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀπέχθεσθαι</foreign> freq. found in codd. should be written <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀπεχθέσθαι, ξφ. ἀπεχθάνομαι.</foreign> </entryFree>"}]}